# SAMPLE TEMPLATE: How to Add a New Talk
# =====================================
# To add a new talk:
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to YYYY-MM-DD-short-title.md (e.g., 2023-01-01-conference-talk.md). The date determines ordering (newest first).
# 2. Edit the YAML front matter below with your details.
# 3. Add the main content after the YAML (e.g., abstract, slides link).
# 4. Place slides/PDFs in /files/ and images in /images/.
# 5. Optional fields: type (e.g., 'Conference Proceeding talk'), venue, location, talk_url (external link), abstract.
# 6. Save and rebuild the site to see it listed under Talks.

